{"tid":2404020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者質疑濫用國安保釋新門檻","createTime":"2021-02-11T12:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T14:19:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7cb62422b52b1974779171ce02a0b3bcd9e5507","tid":2404020,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/OPMA5MZISBFM3JOXI6VWYIXYIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FOPMA5MZISBFM3JOXI6VWYIXYIE%2F&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e0ab63c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210211%2FOPMA5MZISBFM3JOXI6VWYIXYIE%2F&h=205fb1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210211/OPMA5MZISBFM3JOXI6VWYIXYIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n學者質疑濫用國安保釋新門檻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p6IPKl2YKu0UsG6HJZXrox-wG2M=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5KRXGUUPJD7VD63JQ47YDWEUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp6IPKl2YKu0UsG6HJZXrox-wG2M%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5KRXGUUPJD7VD63JQ47YDWEUE.jpg&h=c3637086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張達明<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】控方昨引用國安法第42條於非國安法的罪行，港大法律學院首席講師張達明坦言有保留，認為該例只能「用於違反國安法罪行，唔係其他罪行」。他認為傑斯面對的具有煽動意圖行為罪，應如一般刑事案般享受「保釋假定」等權利，前設是批准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傑斯涉煽動還柙過年  開咪「林鄭死全家」成罪證<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指應按刑事案享保釋假定權<br />\n<br />\n張達明認為，第42條應該只適用於國安法罪行，「講緊係違反國安法」；不過控方現時的做法，「似乎係用緊analogy（類比）嘅方式，話兩類罪行背後嘅精神、法例精神都差唔多，都係涉及危害國家安全、係嚴重嘅」，故將國安法有關保釋的條文應用於非國安法罪行上。惟張達明坦言，能否直接引用第42條，「係一個大問號」，他認為不可直接引用。<br />\n<br />\n他指黎智英案雖就第42條中危害國家安全行為下定義，包括國安法罪行的行為，以及香港法例中涉及維護國家安全罪行的行為，他強調，「運用嘅情況係違反國安法罪行，唔係其他罪行」，非國安法罪行應根據《刑事訴訟程序條例》有關保釋的條文處理，包括享有「保釋假定」（presumption of bail）等權利。<br />\n<br />\n張達明指出，自國安法。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"939d5656d62e0a960c58566a01da665bfbe00d82","tid":2404020,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"唔使質疑啦，擺明"},{"pid":"00c1ef7771acf629185097d8ec54bcc7ef2e73e3","tid":2404020,"uid":365765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"香港法律怎能興天朝混為一談？<br />\n豈不貽笑天下？"},{"pid":"2023fb254c16b823c867a44a7d7f33bade854b81","tid":2404020,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c1ef7771acf629185097d8ec54bcc7ef2e73e3","tid":2404020,"uid":365765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"香港法律怎能興天朝混為一談？<br />\n豈不貽笑天下？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0308b8ad20216c78eb05353795624e14913ba159","tid":2404020,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">林鄭死全家</span>"},{"pid":"725fcf53c14fc7594c6f0d569dfaabdc84c4b906","tid":2404020,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"次次都質疑，有邊次係法庭接納<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e122e893dcec37634692c44ee086695005c6cf5c","tid":2404020,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T14:19:04.000Z","msg":"人地有槍，佢話人獸交先係正統<br />\n<br />\n你都要跪啦"}]}